description: Redevelopment of the site to create 128 residential units (Class C3) including affordable housing and a community use facility (Class D1), following demolition and conversion/refurbishment of existing buildings used for student accommodation and ancillary offices (sui generis) and construction of new buildings ranging between 3 - 5 storeys in height, together with associated works to create basements, car parking, landscaping and public realm improvements.
